title: Encyclopedia of Chemistry - Don Rittner, Ronald A. Bailey
description:
Encyclopedia of Chemistry - Don Rittner, Ronald A. Bailey (Facts On File, 2005).pdf

With a structure that reflects the way chemistry is currently studied, the Encyclopedia of Chemistry has hundreds of chemistry-related entries, thought-provoking essays, leading discoveries, and biographies of notable chemists throughout history. It is written for high school and early college students
